MyBroadband’s 2016 Technology Survey has revealed that WhatsApp is the favourite messaging service of South African techies. The survey was completed by 2,134 respondents, of which 64% were either an IT professional, IT manager, or general techie. Respondents were asked an array of questions, including what are their favourite messaging and social media services. In the social media category, Facebook took top spot. The table below details the results of the 2016 Technology Survey.